Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.85,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.12,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just ignore them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.46,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have time to rescue everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:43.40,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:47.07,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,The station... and Gojo-sensei... \Nare just up ahead, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.14,Main,Toge,0000,0000,0000,,Roe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:49.36,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,That vocabulary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:52.16,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Inumaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:52.94,Main,Toge,0000,0000,0000,,Salmon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.77,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.00,Main,Toge,0000,0000,0000,,Salmon, salmon.
