Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.32,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Yuji Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.32,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,My brothers' killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:38.82,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Convergence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.82,Convergence,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp2\pos(320,265)}Convergence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.20,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Manipulation: "Convergence"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:48.45,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,is a skill that involves applying pressure \Nto blood in order to compress it to its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.92,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The blood compressed with Convergence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.10,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,is then released through a single point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:59.60,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The initial speed of this blood \Nenhanced with cursed energy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.56,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,well exceeds the speed \Nof sound when released.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:06.43,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,This secret art of Blood \NManipulation is called...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.43,Convergence,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp2\pos(320,265)}Piercing Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.44,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.09,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,A double impact?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.77,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,What an odd technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:43.76,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,There's something
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.78,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,I have to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.40,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Did my little brothers leave \Nbehind any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:52.89,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:53.82,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.15,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the ones you two killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.83,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.32,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.74,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,They were crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:12.74,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Eso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.17,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Kechizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:19.09,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Watch over me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:25.01,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,This is your older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.56,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.14,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,He got distance on me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:50.86,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,That beam of blood is too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.64,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I have a 50/50 chance to dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.40,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,If my intuition is off and it hits my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.44,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:01.89,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then I should at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:11.91,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,determine when he fires it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.10,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,He's luring me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.52,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.92,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:39.73,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,That attack is only fast when first fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.95,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Once I avoid it, I can lay on the pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.19,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.19,Convergence,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp2\pos(320,265)}Supernova
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.00,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.09,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,I got hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.87,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't compressed enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.64,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! This bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.97,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:33.96,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.65,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.80,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Mechamaru! What have you been—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.66,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Conserving energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.78,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:45.38,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Choso! Blood Manipulation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:46.18,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,You know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.05,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,He's using the same \Ncursed technique as Kamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.62,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,That thin-eyed third year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.90,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.60,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know its weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.30,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Geh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:09:00.84,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Manipulation is treasured as one of \Nthe Kamo clan's hereditary techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:04.25,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,The reason for that is "Convergence," \Nwhich compresses blood with high pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:08.04,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,plus "Piercing Blood" and "Blood Blade," \Nwhich are derived from that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:11.32,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,giving it a well-balanced response \Nin close, mid, and long range.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.22,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Since Choso won't bleed out, \Nhe has no openings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.82,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the critical infor—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:20.66,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know its weakness, \Nbut I do have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.12,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.01,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,First, flee into the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.64,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,The restroom?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.67,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.93,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's maybe a 10% chance this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:32.68,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but if this fails, \Nbrace yourself for death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:33.87,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.54,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll just get worn \Ndown until you're killed anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.31,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:50.48,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,That only leads to the \Nrestrooms and the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.49,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which you run to, \Nyou're trapped like a rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.02,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.38,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,This guy has beaten my brothers before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.55,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Those two wouldn't lose to some idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:08.30,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,There's also that second voice \Nthat suddenly appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:12.16,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,It would be right to assume \Nhe's planning something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:13.31,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:14.50,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.04,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:19.00,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're a coward, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.24,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just like your brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.77,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.02,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1c&H213835&\3c&H75EFED&\blur20\1a&HE0&\3a&HC0&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.02,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(675,0)\3c&HA0DCE8&\pos(320,18)\c&H292619&}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.40,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,You really are just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.49,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,All three of you care \Nso much for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.61,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you easy to manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.83,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's all gone well so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:52.25,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's up to chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.54,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yuji Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.66,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.19,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,That was your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:14.27,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one with nowhere to run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.60,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Convergence dissolved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:27.33,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,In order to enhance the effects of \Nthe Blood Manipulation Technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.28,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,users constantly have the coagulation \Nproperties of their blood turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:37.29,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, Choso's blood dissolves in \Nwater more easily than that of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:40.96,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, once exposed to water,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:46.41,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,the osmotic pressure causes the red blood \Ncells to expand and rupture their cell walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:53.84,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,This left him unable to control the blood \Ncells that comprise 45% of his blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:56.31,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,breaking his Convergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.76,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Mechamaru's aim was on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.16,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,In that situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:06.71,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,it was impossible for Choso to use \NBlood Manipulation outside his own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:16.77,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Flowing Red Scale - Stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.58,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Choso lacked combat experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:22.84,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,so he couldn't comprehend \Nwhat was happening to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.46,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,He just coldly accepted the new reality
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:28.88,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,and conducted his blood \Nmanipulation within his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:32.28,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.04,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't any opportunity for me to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.86,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,But I do know one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.62,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I've dragged him into my turf!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.52,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:57.09,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Choso had been keeping a clot of blood from being exposed and dissolving
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:14:00.75,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,in the water as he strengthened \Nsaid clot with cursed energy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.96,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,and compressed the \Ncoagulated lump to its limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:08.62,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,so the moment Yuji Itadori \Nwas convinced of victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.37,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,it pierced his liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:15.32,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Manipulation: Blood Meteorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.36,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up! I assumed he couldn't \Nuse any more projectiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.04,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What now? Where was I hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:24.32,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the same as when \NI had a hole in my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.92,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,It destroyed something \Nthat shouldn't be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:28.48,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.93,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:39.85,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what my role is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.68,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Fushiguro, Kugisaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:46.20,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin, the other \Nupperclassmen, all of them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.62,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,will pass through here on \Ntheir way to Gojo-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:53.12,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,So even if I die, I'm taking this guy out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:58.08,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to be the one \Nto rescue Gojo-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:00.96,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Three hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.11,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,A mere three hits,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:05.29,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,not counting the ones I guarded against.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:09.80,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Those blows I took from Itadori \Ndealt this much damage to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.79,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Meteorite's only \Nstrength is its hardness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.60,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have the speed \Nor impact of Piercing Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:20.31,Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't caught him by surprise, \Nit wouldn't have been able to pierce him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.17,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, Blood Manipulation sorcerers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:26.40,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,never coagulate blood like \Nhe did for Blood Meteorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:29.54,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Even Blood Blade only \Nsolidifies the outline and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:33.24,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,circulates blood at high speeds \Nto heighten its lethality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:36.04,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Even those sorcerers with \NBlood Manipulation can't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.08,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,extend their concentration \Nto every blood vessel at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.88,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,So when they strongly coagulate their blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:46.09,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,it always poses the risk of \Ncausing spontaneous thrombosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:47.49,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:55.85,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,However, Choso decided the risk \Nposed by Yuji Itadori was far greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:22.41,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:33.60,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,A tooth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.03,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,It was a feint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.59,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.08,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't used my left fist since the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:59.35,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,He probably believes I can't use it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.81,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,So this attack using my \Nright fist as a distraction
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.39,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,will land!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:14.44,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What was that response I felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.21,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:50.83,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,He's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.75,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:06.01,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,to my brothers in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.27,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,How worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.88,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Losing to such riffraff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.20,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.08,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,In that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.94,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,memories flooded Choso's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.94,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H3B4243&\bord0\shad0}Memories that didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.02,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Memories that didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.76,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:05.99,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:21.41,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening? You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:23.32,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:33.60,Main,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:34.48,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:38.32,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this started, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.24,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Moan-day?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.24,0:23:43.25,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:44.20,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Tuesday!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:45.20,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Mhmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:46.64,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Weh-do-ness-day?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:47.33,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:48.68,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:49.89,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Fluctuations."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:56.66,Next_Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\blur4}Next Episode\N{\fs30\fscy150}Fluctuations
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:52.13,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell came up with these readings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:54.62,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Someone smarter than you, dummy.

